### FedEx API 直接測試文件
### 使用VS Code REST Client擴展執行這些請求

### 1. 獲取Access Token
# @name getToken
POST https://apis-sandbox.fedex.com/oauth/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=client_credentials&client_id=l7c69825ca9b56493eaae0ee89165f7737&client_secret=1bd8453d7444428f8cb905fc36481793

### 2. 使用POST方法查詢貨件列表
# @name searchShipmentsPost
POST https://apis-sandbox.fedex.com/ship/v1/shipments/search
Authorization: Bearer {{getToken.response.body.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-locale: zh_TW

{
  "searchCriteria": {
    "createDateRange": {
      "beginDate": "2025-06-29",
      "endDate": "2025-07-29"
    },
    "accountNumber": {
      "value": "740561073"
    }
  },
  "resultsPerPage": 100,
  "resultOffset": 0
}

### 3. 使用GET方法嘗試查詢 (測試用)
# @name searchShipmentsGet
GET https://apis-sandbox.fedex.com/ship/v1/shipments/search?accountNumber=740561073&beginDate=2025-06-29&endDate=2025-07-29
Authorization: Bearer {{getToken.response.body.access_token}}
Accept: application/json
X-locale: zh_TW

### 4. 嘗試電子商務訂單API (測試用)
# @name ecommerceOrders
GET https://apis-sandbox.fedex.com/commerce/v1/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{getToken.response.body.access_token}}
Accept: application/json
X-locale: zh_TW

### 5. 貨件結果查詢API (使用/ship/v1/shipments/results端點)
# @name shipmentResults
POST https://apis-sandbox.fedex.com/ship/v1/shipments/results
Authorization: Bearer {{getToken.response.body.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-locale: en_US

{
  "searchCriteria": {
    "createDateRange": {
      "beginDate": "2025-06-29",
      "endDate": "2025-07-29"
    },
    "accountNumber": {
      "value": "740561073"
    }
  }
}
